songs.title: Beautiful Memories My Dear
songs.lyrics:
Besides me, you have him!
You have me as a slave
I lie in my bed

Junk programs
Hitting my head

My thoughts rot the little sanity that I have left
In my head your name keeps sounding

I just want to stop pretending something that I'm not

You knew me like an idiot with a smile the whole day (Not even if)
Every time I close my eyes I look at your face
